title: (Tuesday Full Show) Bobby Awards Employee of the Month + Caller Caught Next-door Neighbor Cheating! Bobby Feud: America’s Breakfast Cereals
itunes:title: (Tuesday Full Show) Bobby Awards Employee of the Month + Caller Caught Next-door Neighbor Cheating! Bobby Feud: America’s Breakfast Cereals
description:
We play a round of the Bobby Feud where the show tries to guess what America voted as the Top 10 Cereals! Per listener request, Bobby brings back the Employee of the Month awards. He hands out the title to the person who brought the most to the show in the last month. A caller shares her story of how she caught her neighbor cheating and he confronted her! What does she do next? Plus, Eddie Brings in some secret audio he recorded of someone else on the show.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
